libyan.text: If your pocket gets empty, your faults will be many.
He who searches for pearls should not sleep.
If everyone thought the same way, no goods would ever be sold.
Those who pry into other people's affairs will hear what they do not like.
Each trip gives you its own uniqueness.
If everyone thought the same way, no goods would ever be sold.
A mad dog bites anything except itself.
Each trip gives you its own uniqueness.
If everyone thought the same way, no goods would ever be sold.
If everyone thought alike, no goods would ever be sold.
Stretch your legs according to the length of your bedspread.
